      "span_text": "expression of classic M2 signature genes such as arginase-1 (Arg1), resistinlike molecule alpha (RELMa), mannose receptor (MR) and interleukin-10 (IL10) [CITATION_1] was barely detectable neither as mRNA (Fig. 1a) nor protein (Fig. 1b) ."
